b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":684,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Summon Showcase: Dragon Special Is Now Live!","message":"<div>The Summon Showcase: Dragon Special kicked off <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1566885600\\"><\/span>!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>During this showcase, the appearance rates for featured 4\\u2605 and 5\\u2605 dragons will be boosted.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Regarding Appearance Rate Changes in the Summon Showcase: Dragon Special<br>Starting with this summon showcase, the appearance rates for 5\\u2605 featured dragons, 5\\u2605 featured adventurers, 5\\u2605 dragons, 4\\u2605 featured dragons, and 4\\u2605 featured adventurers in the Summon Showcase: Dragon Special will be changed as detailed below.<br>Note: Adventurers have been removed from the featured group.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fb5\\u2605 featured dragons<\/div><div>Before: 1.50%<\/div><div>After: 2.40%<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fb5\\u2605 featured adventurers<\/div><div>Before: 0.50%<\/div><div>After: 0%<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fb5\\u2605 dragons<\/div><div>Before: 1.25%<\/div><div>After: 0.85%<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fb4\\u2605 featured dragons<\/div><div>Before: 5.25%<\/div><div>After: 7.00%<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fb4\\u2605 featured adventurers<\/div><div>Before: 1.75%<\/div><div>After: 0%<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Dragon Special Appearance Rates:<\/div><div>5\\u2605 featured - Total: 2.40% (Adventurers: 0%, Dragons: 2.4%)<\/div><div>5\\u2605 normal - Total: 1.6% (Adventurers: 0.75%, Dragons: 0.85%)<\/div><div>4\\u2605 featured - Total: 7.00% (Adventurers: 0%, Dragons: 7%)<\/div><div>4\\u2605 normal - Total: 9.00% (Adventurers: 5.05%, Dragons: 3.95%)<\/div><div>3\\u2605 normal - Total: 80.00% (Adventurers: 48.00%, Dragons: 32.00%)<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>This showcase will be available from <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1566885600\\"><